{"tid":1851482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"勞工處呼籲僱主為僱員提供外科口罩等個人防護裝備","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T07:05:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f91f1ae246e1906c1432e3a612aa1f797641673","tid":1851482,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1505632_1_L_20200130130132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1505632_1_L_20200130130132.jpg&h=48a04920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勞工處呼籲僱主，為前線及有需要員工提供外科口罩等個人防護裝備，減低疫情在社區擴散的風險。<br />\n<br />\n就湖北省抵港人士，衞生署要求如沒有任何徵狀，應戴上外科口罩，並繼續佩戴直至離開內地後14天，並應盡量自我隔離14天。若出現發燒或其他病徵，應立即到就近醫院急症室求診，主動告訴醫生最近曾到訪湖北省。<br />\n<br />\n其他從內地回港的市民，返港14天內亦應盡量留在家中；如有需要外出，應佩戴外科口罩，又呼籲僱主應體諒個別僱員的情況，作出彈性工作安排。"},{"pid":"32150f21ab66ee199db9a8a45f7e354c5ce2a259","tid":1851482,"uid":134226,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"政府唔係全港最大僱主咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f8055bdf31501563e560c5d56a07d3e76007f8","tid":1851482,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"完全係無政府狀態<br />\n港共殖民政府唔提供口罩, 叫僱主提供比僱員？<br />\n<br />\n乜勞工處覺得, 假如僱主有大量口罩庫存, <br />\n會唔提供比僱員, 由得係OFFICE大爆發咩？<br />\n有先得架！唔係個個僱主有呀！"},{"pid":"b54c43627f89be4c4da3cead399fef159861b13b","tid":1851482,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"即係咪冇口罩就唔駛返工先?"},{"pid":"f7fb3ae520eebdd094d957076a50f2904eca2da7","tid":1851482,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"32150f21ab66ee199db9a8a45f7e354c5ce2a259","tid":1851482,"uid":134226,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"政府唔係全港最大僱主咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"流傳港共殖民政府口罩存倉地點：<br />\n(1) 柴灣創富道11號政府物料營運中心<br />\n(2) 葵涌冠華鏡廠第三工業大廈"},{"pid":"56acba3709bc4a3d293f9e9e6d141ce28c05df1b","tid":1851482,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"邊撚個議員投票比公務員加人工<br />\n<br />\n我屌到佢2046！"},{"pid":"fc878f3abf49f35c14a9dd0c9b5a353772033802","tid":1851482,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=baed1f72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"80ad07d42a95179892d959808ba4f1512e93338c","tid":1851482,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc878f3abf49f35c14a9dd0c9b5a353772033802","tid":1851482,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></sp